      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-03842'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050223_GCR_79'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gordon-borrie' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050223_GCR_79' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gordon Borrie' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
