            Before I leave the amendment, is the Minister saying with regard to subsection (5) that the ability of the tribunal to award costs to a party to proceedings is limited to vexatious, frivolous or unreasonable conduct in the course of those proceedings? It may not be fair to expect an instant answer to the question&#x2014;I shall be quite content if it comes later&#x2014;but it would help the Committee to know that.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
